评论概述: Floppy, not hard like a military board
评论详情: I only took one star off for this item, and it was because the epaulet is very floppy. It seems to be mounted on a piece of felt. I expected them to be rigid, the way a military epaulet on a mess dress uniform would be. Also, the pins are completely unusable. It would be good if they just put a couple of loops on the back, and you could pin those yourself. But for the money, I just sewed some popsicle sticks to the bottom and covered it with more felt, and then used a really BIG safety pin to mount them initially, and then when I got the exact coat I wanted, I sewed them down properly to the shoulder. All that aside...these are really bright and swingy and very banana republic dictator looking. Other reviews complained about the chains, but mine were mounted well and sturdily.
